[SPEAKER_02] i mogu vam ih sad pozdati,

1200
00:38:03,539 --> 00:38:03,739
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

1201
00:38:03,739 --> 00:38:05,380
[SPEAKER_02] to je članom naše zajednice.

1202
00:38:05,380 --> 00:38:06,440
[SPEAKER_02] Onda su, ono,

1203
00:38:06,440 --> 00:38:06,719
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

1204
00:38:06,719 --> 00:38:08,079
[SPEAKER_02] i iznenađeni,

1205
00:38:08,079 --> 00:38:08,460
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

1206
00:38:08,460 --> 00:38:09,679
[SPEAKER_02] gledaju, pa dobro što se to,

1207
00:38:09,679 --> 00:38:09,860
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

1208
00:38:09,860 --> 00:38:10,599
[SPEAKER_02] još uvijek živi.

1209
00:38:10,599 --> 00:38:11,659
[SPEAKER_02] Oni misle da je to,

1210
00:38:11,659 --> 00:38:12,000
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

1211
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:13,320
[SPEAKER_02] u srednjoj vijeku bilo,

1212
00:38:13,320 --> 00:38:14,400
[SPEAKER_02] ali,

1213
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:16,440
[SPEAKER_02] jako je važna ta suradnja

1214
00:38:16,440 --> 00:38:17,679
[SPEAKER_02] i,

1215
00:38:17,679 --> 00:38:18,460
[SPEAKER_02] i stvarno,

1216
00:38:18,460 --> 00:38:18,760
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

1217
00:38:18,760 --> 00:38:21,420
[SPEAKER_02] baš ovo što je Don Tomo rekao,

1218
00:38:21,420 --> 00:38:22,000
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

1219
00:38:22,480 --> 00:38:25,639
[SPEAKER_02] čovjek danas koji priča mladima,

1220
00:38:25,639 --> 00:38:27,320
[SPEAKER_02] mora biti svjedok.

1221
00:38:27,320 --> 00:38:30,119
[SPEAKER_02] Mora biti svjedok i jednostavno,

1222
00:38:30,119 --> 00:38:30,420
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

1223
00:38:30,420 --> 00:38:31,679
[SPEAKER_02] moramo, ono,

1224
00:38:31,679 --> 00:38:33,239
[SPEAKER_02] moramo svjedočiti mladima,

1225
00:38:33,239 --> 00:38:33,940
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

1226
00:38:33,940 --> 00:38:37,579
[SPEAKER_02] osobne iskustva i što kaže na kraju katekizam katoličke crkve,

1227
00:38:37,579 --> 00:38:40,860
[SPEAKER_02] sakramentalizaciji mora prethoditi evangelizacija.

1228
00:38:40,860 --> 00:38:42,019
[SPEAKER_02] Ono,

1229
00:38:42,019 --> 00:38:43,900
[SPEAKER_02] mi moramo jednostavno, ono,

1230
00:38:43,900 --> 00:38:44,900
[SPEAKER_02] dovesti te mlade,

1231
00:38:44,900 --> 00:38:47,019
[SPEAKER_02] da oni upoznaju,

1232
00:38:47,019 --> 00:38:50,119
[SPEAKER_02] da oni dožive taj susret sa gospodinom,

1233
00:38:50,559 --> 00:38:52,539
[SPEAKER_02] a onda ih polako ulačiti,

1234
00:38:52,539 --> 00:38:52,840
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

1235
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:53,619
[SPEAKER_02] u sakramente,

1236
00:38:53,619 --> 00:38:54,840
[SPEAKER_02] objašnjati ih sakramente.

1237
00:38:54,840 --> 00:38:56,860
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sjećam kak je meni ono bilo na,

1238
00:38:56,860 --> 00:39:00,380
[SPEAKER_02] kad sam išao ko klinac na misu,

1239
00:39:00,380 --> 00:39:00,579
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

1240
00:39:00,579 --> 00:39:02,039
[SPEAKER_02] dođeš tamo i ono brojiš,

1241
00:39:02,039 --> 00:39:02,699
[SPEAKER_02] ovako, ono,

1242
00:39:02,699 --> 00:39:03,679
[SPEAKER_02] gore lampice,

1243
00:39:03,679 --> 00:39:05,019
[SPEAKER_02] brojiš pločice po podu,

1244
00:39:05,019 --> 00:39:05,719
[SPEAKER_02] niš ne znaš.

1245
00:39:05,719 --> 00:39:07,480
[SPEAKER_02] Onda kad ti je došao,

1246
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:08,780
[SPEAKER_02] ko što sam i rekao,

1247
00:39:08,780 --> 00:39:09,199
[SPEAKER_02] Matija,

1248
00:39:09,199 --> 00:39:10,900
[SPEAKER_02] ili neki mlađi lik,

1249
00:39:10,900 --> 00:39:12,099
[SPEAKER_02] koji to stvarno živi,

1250
00:39:12,099 --> 00:39:13,360
[SPEAKER_02] koji ima uvjerenje u to,

1251
00:39:13,360 --> 00:39:14,219
[SPEAKER_02] kojeg, ono,

1252
00:39:14,219 --> 00:39:15,280
[SPEAKER_02] ne možeš poljuljati

1253
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:16,480
[SPEAKER_02] i koji to doživio,

1254
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:18,420
[SPEAKER_02] kad ti ono objasni šta je,

1255
00:39:18,420 --> 00:39:19,519
[SPEAKER_02] šta se tu događa,

1256
00:39:19,519 --> 00:39:21,800
[SPEAKER_02] na kraju kad ti to doživiš,

1257
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:22,300
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

1258
00:39:22,300 --> 00:39:24,440
[SPEAKER_02] to te tjera da ti dođeš na misu,

1259
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:25,739
[SPEAKER_02] da budeš prisutan,

1260
00:39:25,739 --> 00:39:26,000
[SPEAKER_02] ono,

1261
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:28,000
[SPEAKER_02] to te tjera da imaš osobnu molitvu.

1262
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,320
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da, ono,

1263
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:30,800
[SPEAKER_02] ja mislim da je to prevažna stvar,

1264
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:32,139
[SPEAKER_02] suradnja svećenika i...

1265
00:39:32,139 --> 00:39:33,559
[SPEAKER_01] Da, jedan od razloga

1266
00:39:33,559 --> 00:39:34,780
[SPEAKER_01] za kje smo išli u ovu temu

1267
00:39:34,780 --> 00:39:36,059
[SPEAKER_01] i držimo se novima,

1268
00:39:36,059 --> 00:39:38,519
[SPEAKER_01] malo stari i mladima,

1269
00:39:38,519 --> 00:39:39,559
[SPEAKER_01] znači, govorimo nekakva

1270
00:39:39,559 --> 00:39:40,179
[SPEAKER_01] srednja škola,

1271
00:39:40,179 --> 00:39:41,280
[SPEAKER_01] početak faksa je to,

1272
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:44,039
[SPEAKER_01] je zato kje smo skužili

1273
00:39:44,039 --> 00:39:46,820
[SPEAKER_01] da mlađa djeca,

1274
00:39:46,820 --> 00:39:47,920
[SPEAKER_01] baš djeca,

1275
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:48,960
[SPEAKER_01] ono, vrtić,

1276
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:50,260
[SPEAKER_01] početak osnovne škole,

1277
00:39:50,260 --> 00:39:53,300
[SPEAKER_01] tu je više stvar odgoja

1278
00:39:53,300 --> 00:39:54,739
[SPEAKER_01] i njih roditelji imaju

1279
00:39:54,739 --> 00:39:55,860
[SPEAKER_01] nekak pod kontrolom.

1280
00:39:55,860 --> 00:39:57,500
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, tu djecu možeš,

1281
00:39:57,500 --> 00:39:58,639
[SPEAKER_01] ako je mama,

1282
00:39:58,639 --> 00:40:00,599
[SPEAKER_01] ima mogućnost biti doma,

1283
00:40:00,780 --> 00:40:03,199
[SPEAKER_01] pa ih ona oblikuje,

1284
00:40:03,199 --> 00:40:04,539
[SPEAKER_01] možeš ih upisati u,

1285
00:40:04,539 --> 00:40:06,559
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, katolički vrtić,

1286
00:40:06,559 --> 00:40:08,559
[SPEAKER_01] možeš ih upisati u katoličku osnovnu,

1287
00:40:08,559 --> 00:40:09,519
[SPEAKER_01] okej, ima je srednjih,

1288
00:40:09,519 --> 00:40:12,139
[SPEAKER_01] ali tu ih još nekak ti sam

1289
00:40:12,139 --> 00:40:13,260
[SPEAKER_01] možeš uokvirit.

1290
00:40:13,260 --> 00:40:16,860
[SPEAKER_01] Kasnije, adolescenti,

1291
00:40:16,860 --> 00:40:20,500
[SPEAKER_01] više ih nemaš toliko pod kontrolom.

1292
00:40:20,500 --> 00:40:22,099
[SPEAKER_01] Dođe krizma,

1293
00:40:22,099 --> 00:40:23,699
[SPEAKER_01] obično se zna ono,

1294
00:40:23,699 --> 00:40:24,780
[SPEAKER_01] sarkastična reč,

1295
00:40:24,780 --> 00:40:26,539
[SPEAKER_01] vidimo se na, ne znam,

1296
00:40:26,539 --> 00:40:27,880
[SPEAKER_01] vinčanju ili tako nešto.

1297
00:40:29,980 --> 00:40:31,340
[SPEAKER_01] meni je zanima,

1298
00:40:31,340 --> 00:40:37,219
[SPEAKER_01] kak te koji se odvoje,

1299
00:40:37,219 --> 00:40:38,579
[SPEAKER_01] nas koji smo se odvojili

1300
00:40:38,579 --> 00:40:39,320
[SPEAKER_01] nakon krizme,

1301
00:40:39,320 --> 00:40:40,500
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam bio taj,

1302
00:40:40,500 --> 00:40:42,960
[SPEAKER_01] kaj ih najviše privuće?

1303
00:40:42,960 --> 00:40:44,400
[SPEAKER_01] Da li postoje,

1304
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:46,260
[SPEAKER_01] recimo, crkva organiziruje jako puno

1305
00:40:46,260 --> 00:40:46,960
[SPEAKER_01] kampova,

1306
00:40:46,960 --> 00:40:47,719
[SPEAKER_01] ljetnih kampova,

1307
00:40:47,719 --> 00:40:49,980
[SPEAKER_01] postoji oratori koji je otvoren

1308
00:40:49,980 --> 00:40:51,880
[SPEAKER_01] pet, šest, sedam dana na runu.

1309
00:40:52,820 --> 00:40:56,119
[SPEAKER_01] Kaj ih najlakše privuće?

1310
00:40:56,119 --> 00:40:56,900
[SPEAKER_01] Jesu to kampovi,

1311
00:40:56,900 --> 00:40:57,619
[SPEAKER_01] jesu to oratori?

1312
00:40:57,619 --> 00:41:00,119
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to možda običan susret sa mladima,

1313
00:41:00,119 --> 00:41:02,360
[SPEAKER_01] pa on ima nekakvu teškoću,

1314
00:41:02,360 --> 00:41:05,179
[SPEAKER_01] pa mu se ti pokažeš kao neko ko bez interesa mu želi pomoći?

1315
00:41:05,179 --> 00:41:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kaj ste vidjeli svom razu

1316
00:41:06,480 --> 00:41:08,320
[SPEAKER_01] da najlakše privuće mlade

1317
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:09,119
[SPEAKER_01] nakon što su,

1318
00:41:09,119 --> 00:41:09,920
[SPEAKER_01] na primjer,

1319
00:41:09,920 --> 00:41:10,860
[SPEAKER_01] nakon krizme otišli?

1320
00:41:13,260 --> 00:41:20,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ako svećenik ću pričati,

1321
00:41:20,340 --> 00:41:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] sigurno sve te ispovjede,

1322
00:41:21,960 --> 00:41:23,739
[SPEAKER_00] ono, iskustvo sve te ispovjedi,

1323
00:41:23,739 --> 00:41:24,860
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam,

1324
00:41:24,860 --> 00:41:27,420
[SPEAKER_00] ili trebaju biti kumovi,

1325
00:41:27,420 --> 00:41:29,239
[SPEAKER_00] ili, ne znam,

1326
00:41:29,239 --> 00:41:31,139
[SPEAKER_00] nešto ih,

1327
00:41:31,139 --> 00:41:32,860
[SPEAKER_00] da, nešto ih,

1328
00:41:32,860 --> 00:41:33,920
[SPEAKER_00] ono, znaju ljudi,

1329
00:41:33,920 --> 00:41:36,719
[SPEAKER_00] nisam mogao više, nešto me potaknulo

1330
00:41:36,719 --> 00:41:37,599
[SPEAKER_00] da dođem to,

1331
00:41:37,599 --> 00:41:38,900
[SPEAKER_00] i ona dođu na ispovjedi,

1332
00:41:38,900 --> 00:41:40,900
[SPEAKER_00] ono, dožive na ispovjedi baš neko, ono,

1333
00:41:40,900 --> 00:41:42,800
[SPEAKER_00] povratak neki,

1334
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:44,340
[SPEAKER_00] ono, ja s tim ljudima,

1335
00:41:44,340 --> 00:41:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] to je s tim mladima koji se nisu pojedili dugo,

1336
00:41:46,599 --> 00:41:48,460
[SPEAKER_00] ono, kažem, prvo dobrodošao u kući,

1337
00:41:48,460 --> 00:41:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] a onda sve ostalo.

1338
00:41:49,500 --> 00:41:53,139
[SPEAKER_00] To je sigurno možda najmoćnija stvar,

1339
00:41:53,139 --> 00:41:54,440
[SPEAKER_00] jer ono, tu baš osjete,

1340
00:41:54,440 --> 00:41:56,400
[SPEAKER_00] ono, Boga koji im, ono, oprašta,

1341
00:41:56,400 --> 00:41:58,159
[SPEAKER_00] bez obzira što su se udaljeli,

1342
00:41:58,159 --> 00:42:00,519
[SPEAKER_00] i koji je sretniji od njih,

1343
00:42:00,519 --> 00:42:02,280
[SPEAKER_00] što su se vratili, nek što su oni, evo.

1344
00:42:02,280 --> 00:42:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] To sigurno, onda druga stvar,

1345
00:42:05,500 --> 00:42:09,480
[SPEAKER_00] ti, naravno, ti kampovi, oratori,

1346
00:42:09,480 --> 00:42:12,400
[SPEAKER_00] koji nisu privlačni samo,

1347
00:42:12,739 --> 00:42:14,900
[SPEAKER_00] onima koji su ostali u crkvi,

1348
00:42:14,900 --> 00:42:17,099
[SPEAKER_00] nego i onima koji nisu toliko u crkvi.

1349
00:42:17,159 --> 00:42:18,599
[SPEAKER_00] Je li dolaze mladi van crkve?

1350
00:42:18,599 --> 00:42:21,400
[SPEAKER_01] Pitam zato kaj,

1351
00:42:21,400 --> 00:42:24,539
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam išao na jedan ljetni kamp,

1352
00:42:24,539 --> 00:42:26,139
[SPEAKER_01] kod Don Damirana Postorje,

1353
00:42:26,139 --> 00:42:27,519
[SPEAKER_01] ali sjećam se da je moja prva reakcija

1354
00:42:27,519 --> 00:42:29,980
[SPEAKER_01] tih prvih par puta kad su me zvali,

1355
00:42:29,980 --> 00:42:31,400
[SPEAKER_01] bilo, pa dobro,

1356
00:42:31,400 --> 00:42:32,679
[SPEAKER_01] ljetovanje s crkvom,

1357
00:42:32,679 --> 00:42:34,679
[SPEAKER_01] stvarno, sa svećenikom,

1358
00:42:34,679 --> 00:42:36,300
[SPEAKER_01] pa kao nije to za ili sirotinju,

1359
00:42:36,300 --> 00:42:39,659
[SPEAKER_01] ili ono, za ljude koji stvarno nemaju

1360
00:42:39,659 --> 00:42:40,800
[SPEAKER_01] s nikim otići na more,

1361
00:42:40,940 --> 00:42:42,500
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda ajde svi u grupi,

1362
00:42:42,500 --> 00:42:44,340
[SPEAKER_01] vas 40 koji nema prijatelja,

1363
00:42:44,340 --> 00:42:45,380
[SPEAKER_01] pa ćete se međusobno družiti.

1364
00:42:45,380 --> 00:42:46,780
[SPEAKER_01] Ili stvarno,

1365
00:42:46,780 --> 00:42:48,860
[SPEAKER_01] dolaze mladi van crkve,

1366
00:42:48,860 --> 00:42:51,260
[SPEAKER_01] ili mislim koji nisu već unutra

1367
00:42:51,260 --> 00:42:53,159
[SPEAKER_00] u oratoriju ili u zajednici?

1368
00:42:53,780 --> 00:42:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] Pa dolaze, mislim dolaze kampovi,

1369
00:42:56,500 --> 00:42:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] to koliko god je sa crkvom

1370
00:42:58,119 --> 00:42:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] i sa svećenikom,

1371
00:42:59,019 --> 00:43:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] pe na neki način privlačno je,

1372
00:43:00,559 --> 00:43:02,460
[SPEAKER_00] još bude niža cijena,

1373
00:43:02,460 --> 00:43:04,900
[SPEAKER_00] ono danas za ljetovat pod navodnike,

1374
00:43:04,900 --> 00:43:07,099
[SPEAKER_00] ti ono previsoke su cijena,

1375
00:43:07,099 --> 00:43:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] ono ti imaš kamp sad na prviću

1376
00:43:09,340 --> 00:43:11,519
[SPEAKER_00] ili na postiri za tako nisku cijenu,

1377
00:43:11,519 --> 00:43:12,679
[SPEAKER_00] pa idem, šta me briga,

1378
00:43:12,679 --> 00:43:14,179
[SPEAKER_00] ne trebam ja previše ulaziti

1379
00:43:14,179 --> 00:43:15,760
[SPEAKER_00] u to što oni rade.

1380
00:43:15,760 --> 00:43:17,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ubitno mogu s jednom daje.

1381
00:43:17,139 --> 00:43:19,059
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da, i to, i nekad bude to,

1382
00:43:19,059 --> 00:43:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] neki okidači ono dođu

1383
00:43:20,880 --> 00:43:23,340
[SPEAKER_00] i onda, ono, se promijene na tom kampu

1384
00:43:23,340 --> 00:43:25,900
[SPEAKER_00] i oratori sam po sebi,

1385
00:43:25,900 --> 00:43:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] ono, Dombosko je rekao,

1386
00:43:27,460 --> 00:43:29,900
[SPEAKER_00] ono, volite ono što vole mladi

1387
00:43:29,900 --> 00:43:32,139
[SPEAKER_00] da bi mladi zavoli ono što vi volite,

1388
00:43:32,139 --> 00:43:34,559
[SPEAKER_00] to jest, ono, u smislu,

1389
00:43:34,559 --> 00:43:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] stolni tenis, stolni nogomet,

1390
00:43:36,619 --> 00:43:37,739
[SPEAKER_00] nogomet glazba,

1391
00:43:37,739 --> 00:43:39,659
[SPEAKER_00] ambijent za druženje,

1392
00:43:39,659 --> 00:43:41,800
[SPEAKER_00] pokraj crkve mi imamo tamo oratori,

1393
00:43:41,800 --> 00:43:43,219
[SPEAKER_00] svaku večer je otvoren

1394
00:43:43,219 --> 00:43:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] i dođu mladi koji nisu toliko u vjeri

1395
00:43:46,599 --> 00:43:48,179
[SPEAKER_00] i onda malo pomalo s njima

1396
00:43:48,179 --> 00:43:50,739
[SPEAKER_00] dođeš do tih stvari koje ti voliš,

1397
00:43:50,820 --> 00:43:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno vjera,

1398
00:43:51,559 --> 00:43:53,280
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno vrijednosti neke

1399
00:43:53,280 --> 00:43:55,480
[SPEAKER_00] sveta misa, sveta ispovjedi i to.

1400
00:43:55,480 --> 00:43:56,840
